CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 12, 1957, pg. A15 reads: "Sara Lou whose model figure excites wolf calls from the boys, got the huzzahs from the girls at the Penn-Sheraton Hotel Saturday night when she wore this form-fitting daytime tweed."
TitMainTitle: Sara Lou Harris standing against light colored backdrop, modeling tweed two piece for fashion show sponsored by the Pittsburgh National Council of Negro Women, Penn Sheraton Hotel
